This revision weakens the obligation of Business Third Parties to pay certain fees to TELKOM, as it introduces the possibility for informal extensions of credits or discounts, and shifts the responsibility of paying royalties or fees for additional functionality, enhancements, or value-added services not directly related to the SOFTWARE, to TELKOM. Additionally, it expands the types of revenue that are excluded from this agreement.
